  "title": "Warehouse Assistant [Inventory | West]",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1155459]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Receive and issue spare parts and consumables in accordance with company SOPs, ensuring accurate documentation.</li><li>Safely perform vehicle loading and unloading activities.</li><li>Conduct monthly stock checks to maintain inventory accuracy and availability.</li><li>Participate in annual stock counts to ensure proper asset accountability.</li><li>Perform diesel top-ups for maintenance vehicles.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in warehouse and inventory management.</li><li>Valid Forklift Operator license and Class 4 Vehicle Driving License.</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Felicia Chiam Kar Min<br />EA Personnel Reg. No.: R25152370<br />EA Licence No.: 07C5771 </p>",
